data.name: XModel
desc: represent an XForms model

methods.name: cloneBinding
desc: clone an arbitrary binding element for this model; still needs
The returned binding still needs to be inserted into the bindings container.

methods.name: cloneSubmission
desc: clone an arbitrary submission element for this model
The returned submission element still needs to be inserted into the submission container.

methods.name: createBinding
desc: create a binding element for this model
The returned binding still needs to be inserted into the bindings container.

methods.name: createSubmission
desc: create a submission element for this model
The returned submission element still needs to be inserted into the submission container.

methods.name: getBinding
desc: get a binding with a certain ID
This is a convenience method: the same result can also be obtained through getBindings()

methods.name: getBindings
desc: get a container containing all bindings; also supports XNameAccess

methods.name: getDataTypeRepository
desc: provides management access to the XSD data types associated with the model

methods.name: getDefaultInstance
desc: get the default instance for this model

methods.name: getID
desc: get the XForms model ID

methods.name: getInstanceDocument
desc: retrieves the instance with the given id

methods.name: getInstances
desc: gets container containing all instances;
The elements of the set are arrays of com.sun.star.beans.PropertyValues, containing the ID, the URL, and the instance itself.

methods.name: getSubmission
desc: get a submission with a certain ID.
This is a convenience method: the same result can also be obtained through getSubmissions().

methods.name: getSubmissions
desc: get container containing all submissions; also supports XNameAccess

methods.name: initialize
desc: initialize the model

methods.name: rebuild
desc: rebuild the model

methods.name: recalculate
desc: re-evaluate all calculate attributes

methods.name: refresh
desc: refresh the model

methods.name: revalidate
desc: re-evaluate all validity attributes

methods.name: setID
desc: set the XForms model ID

methods.name: submit
desc: submit form through given submission id
This is a convenience method. Calling it is equivalent to calling getSubmission()( id ).submit().

methods.name: submitWithInteraction
desc: submit form through given submission id
This is a convenience method. Calling it is equivalent to calling getSubmission()( id, handler ).submit().
